flowchart TD
    A[Create Company Request] --> B[Validate JWT Token]
    B --> C{Token Valid?}
    C -->|No| D[Return 401 Unauthorized]
    C -->|Yes| E[Check Admin Permissions]
    E --> F{Admin Access?}
    F -->|No| G[Return 403 Forbidden]
    F -->|Yes| H[Validate Request Data]
    H --> I{Valid Company Data?}
    I -->|No| J[Return 400 Invalid Data]
    I -->|Yes| K[Check Company Name Uniqueness]
    K --> L{Name Available?}
    L -->|No| M[Return 409 Name Already Exists]
    L -->|Yes| N[Generate Company ID]
    N --> O[Create Database Partition]
    O --> P[Insert Company Record]
    P --> Q[Setup Default Configurations]
    Q --> R[Create Admin User]
    R --> S[Initialize Company Cache]
    S --> T[Log Company Creation Event]
    T --> U[Return 201 Company Created]
    
    style A fill:#e1f5fe
    style D fill:#ffebee
    style G fill:#ffebee
    style J fill:#ffebee
    style M fill:#ffebee
    style U fill:#e8f5e8